*** Instructions to use HLT Run-3 tracking customisation ***

** In CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6 (to allow to run also in samples with updated PU profile, e.g., /RelValTTbar_14TeV/CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6-PU_120X_mcRun3_2021_realistic_v4_JIRA_129-v1/GEN-SIM-DIGI-RAW):

cmsrel CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6
pushd CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6/src/
cmsenv
git cms-init
git cms-addpkg HLTrigger/Configuration
git cms-addpkg CommonTools/RecoAlgos
git cms-remote add mmasciov
git fetch mmasciov
git merge mmasciov/forRun3HLTTracking_12X
scram b -j 12

** Example of hltGetConfiguration command:
hltGetConfiguration /dev/CMSSW_12_0_0/GRun --paths HLTriggerFirstPath,MC_ReducedIterativeTracking_v12,HLTriggerFinalPath --offline --mc --unprescale --process TEST --globaltag 120X_mcRun3_2021_realistic_v4 --output none --input /store/relval/CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6/RelValTTbar_14TeV/GEN-SIM-DIGI-RAW/PU_120X_mcRun3_2021_realistic_v4-v1/00000/20a08d38-8b7f-4ce4-b24b-edc023ddd078.root --era Run3 --customise HLTrigger/Configuration/customizeHLTforRun3Tracking.customizeHLTforRun3Tracking

* In order to use quadruplets from ALL pixel vertices (instead of hltTrimmedPixelVertices): HLTrigger/Configuration/customizeHLTforRun3Tracking.customizeHLTforRun3TrackingAllPixelVertices

* Tested using MC_ReducedIterativeTracking_v12 and MC_PFMET_v17



** In release other than CMSSW_12_0_0_pre6:

git cms-remote add mmasciov
git fetch mmasciov
git cherry-pick ee03aa936d3246ae43d093479120f2d3315f7bdf # only needed to use quadruplets from ALL pixel vertices
git cherry-pick cbbe7b2f13e0529868a632b44811de0e753e0562 # to get actual customisation functions
scram b -j 12
